                <p>This part gives the description of my work experience that I have acquired from the project entitled as <strong>“CONSTRUCTION OF THE ELECTRICAL SYSTEM AT AN APARTMENT”. </strong>I was designated as an Electrical Engineer in the company Nico Info Systems India. I served this company September 2014 to April 2018. However, for this project, I worked for the client company Liberty Engineering Equipment Pt. Ltd., which is located in Hyderabad.</p>
